can Party (United States)\n  |candidate  = [[Arlan Stangeland]]\n  |votes      = \n  |percentage = 46\n  |change     = -}}\n{{Election box end}}\n\n==Personal life==\nPeterson lives in [[Detroit Lakes, Minnesota|Detroit Lakes]], just east of Moorhead. He is divorced and previously dated former Congresswoman [[Katherine Harris]], the former Republican [[Secretary of State of Florida]].<ref name=sobig/> He is a licensed private pilot and frequently travels by private plane across his district.<ref name=snapshot/><ref name=sobig/>\n\n==See also==\n* [[US Congressional Delegations from Minnesota]]\n* [[List of United States Representatives from Minnesota]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|33em}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://collinpeterson.house.gov/ Congressman Collin Peterson] official U.S. House site\n*[http://www.petersonforcongress.com/ Peterson for Congress]\n\n{{MN-legdb|10524}}\n\n*{{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Minnesota/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Collin_Peterson_%5BD-7%5D}}\n{{CongLinks | congbio = p000258 | ballot = Collin_Peterson | nndb = 098/000039978 | votesmart = 26926 | govtrack = 400316 | opencong = 400316 | rollcall = 264 | politifact = | fec = H2MN07014 | opensecrets = N00004558 | followthemoney = | assets = collin-peterson | legistorm = 418/Rep_Collin_Clark_Peterson.html | ontheissues = House/Collin_Peterson.htm | congress = collin-peterson/910 | worldcat = np-peterson,%20collin%20c%24collin%20clark%241944 | cspan = 23978 | rose = | imdb = 5000550 | bloomberg = collin-peterson | nyt = | washpo = gIQAIQ6GAP  }}\n*[http://www.leg.state.mn.us/legdb/fulldetail.asp?ID=10524 Political profile] at the Minnesota Legislative Reference Library\n*[http://minnesota.publicradio.org/projects/ongoing/select_a_candidate/cand_positions.php?race_id=21&cand_id=71 Campaign 2012 Candidate Questionnaire] profile from ''[[Minnesota Public Radio]]''\n*[http://www.govtrack.us/congress/bill.xpd?bill=h109-884 Agricultural Job Opportunities, Bene